    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p>The twelve <strong>Earthly Branches</strong> (<span class="chinese-char">地支</span>, Dizhi) represent the receptive, hidden, terrestrial dimension. Each branch corresponds to a <a href="/zodiac/">zodiac animal</a> and carries one or more "hidden stems" — elements concealed within the branch that influence the pillar's total energy:</p>

